claim: Leonardo da Vinci is dating one of the greatest painters of all time.
premise_source_doc_sentence: In his foreword for the book `` Carlo Pedretti - A Bibliography of His Work On Leonardo da Vinci And The Renaissance  (  1944-1984  )  '' , compiled by Joyce Ludmer , famed art historian Kenneth Clark states : `` He  (  Pedretti  )  is unquestionably the greatest Leonardo scholar of our time ... ''
